as trusts</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">’</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> delegated authority to dispose of assets, or to write</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">-</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">off debts. The FNTI will also set out specific actions that the trust needs to take to deal with the cause of the EFA’s concerns, such as recover from a deficit. The EFA will always publish FNTIs and t</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">he reports of investigations. </span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 21.3pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-21.3pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="64" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 21.3pt; orphans:0; text-indent:0pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">Our strong financial accountability regime allows immediate action to be taken. </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">At King’s Science Academy, where we unearthed serious financial concerns, we notified the police, are recovering the funds and have required the</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> school to urgently address all failings.</span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 21.3pt; orphans:0; text-indent:-21.3pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">We have a robust</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold"> system for assessing sponsors and free school proposers</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">,</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold"> but we also provide support to build capacity</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">.</span></p><